text: Juan Rieckehoff (born 20 May 1953) is a Puerto Rican equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Puerto Rican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Puerto Rico Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
